### 🏃 Quick Start

#### Prerequisites

- Claude Code or compatible AI assistant
- Basic understanding of mechanical design

#### Installation

1. Copy this skill to your Claude skills directory:

   ```bash
   cp -r 机械设计指导 ~/.claude/skills/
   ```

2. Restart your Claude Code

3. Start using it:

   > "Help me design a linear motion system"
   > "Calculate the motor size for my conveyor"
   > "Generate a BOM for my robotic arm"

